VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'actually something profoundly different. Um with and and capturing it with the notion of GEM I think is is a is amazing to kind of understand. So, thank you for that. &gt;&gt; I feel the need to just put a disclaimer out there that we\'re not sponsored by'

