VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it. The other right schema, they\'re using LLM\'s.text. All of these little hacks that are just incremental changes to make it easier for an LLM crawler, an agent to learn'

[21:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'about your brand. But no one\'s asking what they should be learning. And no one\'s asking a question particularly to a CMO or head of marketing, if you had to distill the reason to recommend your brand to'

