[22:05] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'you\'ve got to find something unique about your brand that isn\'t purely factual or always on sale or isn\'t purely emotional, we believe in an abstract idea. Because these models are going to be the filter, they\'re the'

